beer.beer_description: Weâ€™ve cracked the code to low ABV and high flavor! CodeName is a Hazy Session IPA that features bright tropical aromas, brilliant citrusy flavors of grapefruit and guava, and a smooth finish.

This light-bodied beer is golden in hue, with fruity tropical aromas of guava, mango, as well as some dank pine, and herbaceous spice. Flavors of biscuit and bread dough balanced with fresh oranges and grapefruit zest are complemented by a clean bitterness. There is a dank quality in this beer that is reminiscent of a west coast style while maintaining the juicy characters akin to east coast IPA. Extremely refreshing, and balanced. Perfect for crushing during an Apres session!
